			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">For Sale: Shark Jaw, Tiger Claw, Fish Maw</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">With little enforcement or legal culpability, social media helps wildlife trafficking thrive in plain sight.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/marina-wang/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Marina Wang</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
